程序包 com.example.books4share

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AcceptActivity
    If the users click on the notification, this activity will show up to let user choose to accept the request or decline the request
    AddBookActivity
    This class is used to add a new book to the book bank
    App
    This class is used to initialize the QR scan tools that we import from ZXingLibrary ZXingLibrary is an open-source, 1D/2D barcode image processing library implemented in Java https://github.com/yipianfengye/android-zxingLibrary
    BookDetailActivity
    Shows the detail of a book
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    Login
    This class is used to do the login part
    MainActivity
    Initiate the home page with add book function and 4 bottom navigation buttons
    MapActivity
    Open a map that allows user to select the location
    ProfileDialogFragment
    This part allows users to edit their profile
    ProfileUser
    This class is user's contact information
    ScanDetailActivity
    Open the camera and scan
    SignInfo
    This part reads the signin information
    Signup
    This class does the signup function
    Users
    The users class defines user properties and methods
    ViewRequestActivity
    This class shows all the incoming requests and outgoing requests
    WelcomeActivity
    This class shows the first page with sign up and log in buttons
    WelcomeTest
